<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Damascus, 20 May (SANA)--Jacob Kleinberger, Swiss 
secretary of state for foreign affairs, left Damascus at noon 
today after a three-day visit to Syria, during which he met with 
