<F P=106> [Unattributed report in the "Provincial Chronicle" column] </F>
  [Text] Yaroslavl -- Russian Federation Vice Premier Yuriy 
Yarov, who arrived at the oblast center 27 April on a working 
visit, went to a number of industrial enterprises and met with 
the leadership of the oblast administration. During the 
meetings the employment problem was discussed. Mr. Yarov 
explained his visit to Yaroslavl by the government's intention 
to study the situation in the regions and try and "see, in good 
time, the line beyond which a social explosion could follow." 

