<H3> <TI>   State Duma Recommends Rejection of Draft Budget </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    State Duma Recommends Rejection of Draft Budget </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2904142494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0605 GMT 
29 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2904142494 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On Wednesday the State Duma Committee for Economic 
Policy drew up a recommendation on a draft of the Russian 
federal budget for 1994. It proposes that the document should 
be rejected because it does not take into account a large number 
of the proposals made by the State Duma committees. The draft 
budget, which was sent to the State Duma, was elaborated by the 
government in accordance with a decision of the lower chamber of 
the parliament of 15 April. The committee's main arguments show 
that the amendments introduced into the budget strengthen the 
orientation of the government's economic policy on the 
preferential development of raw material industries without 
solving problems in other spheres of the economy. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

