  [Text] Colonel General Ihor Sergeyev, commander in chief of 
Ukraine's strategic missile troops, said in Moscow this morning 
that Ukraine is fulfilling its obligations and is transferring 
its nuclear warheads to Russia according to schedule. Already 
180 Ukrainian warheads have been transferred to Russia. In 
return, fuel elements for nuclear power stations have been 
delivered to Ukraine. 

