<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS diplomatic correspondent Anatoliy </F>
Krasnov] 
  [Text] Moscow 29 April TASS -- Russian-South Korean 
relations are definitely on the rise, declared Russian Foreign 
Minister Andrey Kozyrev at a meeting with South Korean Defence 
Minister Yi Pyong-tae, who is in Moscow on an official visit. 
  "I am glad that the military aspect is being given due 
attention in our relations. Now, we are not only not looking at 
