<H3> <TI>   Zhirinovskiy To Begin Visit to Yugoslavia 8 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Zhirinovskiy To Begin Visit to Yugoslavia 8 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3004161594 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1327 GMT 30 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD3004161594 </F>
