<H3> <TI>   New Interior Minister Ramil Usubov Profiled </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Interior Minister Ramil Usubov Profiled </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2904203394 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2904203394 </F>
<F P=104>  Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network </F>

<F P=105>  Azeri </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Here is a short profile of the new interior minister 
appointed by presidential decree. Ramil Idris ogly Usubov was 
born in Khodzhaly in 1948. Since the 1970's he has been working 
in the police organs. He was the interior minister of 
Nakhichevan Autonomous Republic [NAR] in the years 1987-89. He 
served as the head of the passports and visa department and then 
as the head of a desk in the personnel department at the 
Interior Ministry until June 1993. He has been working again as 
the interior minister of NAR since June 1993. He is a lawyer by 
profession, and a graduate of the police academy. He is married 
and has three children. 

</TEXT>

