<H3> <TI>   Kravchuk Decree Mandates Improving Legal Reform </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kravchuk Decree Mandates Improving Legal Reform </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3004040894 Kiev UT-1 Television Network in Ukrainian 1800 
GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3004040894 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UT-1 Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ukraine's president has issued a decree on improving 
the preparation of draft laws and conducting legal reform. In 
accordance with the decree, Ukraine's Ministry of Justice is 
additionally charged with organizing work on elaborating the 
concepts of draft legislative laws on the most important issues 
of the development of society and the state, their scientific 
argumentation, and the coordination of the activity of the 
central bodies of state executive power, scientific 
organizations, and higher education establishments of Ukraine in 
the area of preparing draft laws. 
  Ukraine's Cabinet of Ministers has been instructed to 
organize the work of the legal reform center and draft 
legislative work at Ukraine's Ministry of Justice within a 
period of two months. 

</TEXT>

