<H3> <TI>   Cabinet Decides To Index Vouchers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Cabinet Decides To Index Vouchers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3004030594 Kiev UT-1 Television Network in Ukrainian 1800 
GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3004030594 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UT-1 Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Among the events that could have a fairly noticeable 
effect on our further life is the decision by Ukraine's Cabinet 
of Ministers on the indexation of the nominal value of 
accommodation vouchers. Their value has been established at 
420,000 karbovantsi. Further indexation is to be carried out in 
proportion to changes in the nominal value of privatization 
property certificates. At the same time, the new value of the 
vouchers should be 40 percent of the new value of the 
certificates. 

