<F P=100> Tajikistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Russian Border Guards Thwart Attempted Breakthroughs </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Border Guards Thwart Attempted Breakthroughs </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3004123594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1115 
GMT 30 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3004123594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] </F>
  [Text] Dushanbe, 30 Apr -- A clash between Russian border 
guards and an armed group of Tajik fighters trying to make their 
way into Tajikistan from Afghanistan occurred last night in the 
Shuroabad sector of the Moskovskiy border detachment. According 
to infomation from military sources in Dushanbe, the Russian 
border guards used heavy weapons to repulse the breakthrough. 
The number of dead among the intruders is not being given, 
while there were no casualties among the border guards. 
  Also last night, an attempt by a large party of armed 
intruders from Afghanistan to cross into Tajikistan was thwarted 
by Russian border guards in a sector of the border near the 
village of Porshnev in the Pamir mountains. 

</TEXT>

