<F P=102>   LD3004171894 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 0030 
GMT 30 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3004171894 </F>
<F P=104>  Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network </F>
<F P=105>  Tajik </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A report was broadcast yesterday by the news program 
of the Ostankino television that the situation on the border in 
Badakhshan allegedly became tense, which has resulted in clashes 
between the border guards and the Tajik opposition fighters from 
the other side of the river [in Afghanistan]. 
  According to a report by our correspondent from the 
executive 
committee of the oblast and the military unit of the border 
guards of Badakhshan, this report is groundless and is a mere 
lie. In general, such reports could destabilize the situation 
and become the source for false rumors. The situation in 
Badakhshan and its bordering areas is calm. 

</TEXT>

