<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   U.S. Officials Arrive for Economic Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    U.S. Officials Arrive for Economic Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS0205144294 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 1400 GMT 2 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS0205144294 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A U.S. economic delegation arrived in Kiev today. 
The delegation includes representatives of the U.S. State 
Department, corporate circles, banking institutions, and legal 
experts. The visitors wish to acquaint themselves with the 
progress of market reforms in Ukraine, which will help them 
pinpoint the main directions of U.S. aid to our country. The 
visit's agenda includes meetings with the Ukrainian president's 
administration and other high-ranking officials. Also planned 
are negotiations with the leadership of the National Bank and 
the Association of Ukrainian Commercial Banks. On 5 May, the 
delegation members are going to organize a round-table meeting 
with prominent Ukrainian economists. 

</TEXT>

