  [Text] A resolution issued at a rally of representatives 
of trade unions and working collectives in the city of Grodno 
and Grodno Rayon, sounded like a serious warning to the 
Belarusian Government and Supreme Soviet. Given the 
exacerbation of the economic crisis, they demand that urgent, 
