and relations in the social sector, ensuring a decrease in 
retail prices, the liquidation of crime and corruption, and the 
termination of the illegal redistribution of state property -- 
be undertaken. There are many reasons for this to be done. 
There is a big gap between the consumer basket and actual wages. 

